    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test Conditions factor achieving gradation 2 against a required level of 3. The single-condition deficiency is judged acceptable given the narrow COU scope restricted to the ASTM F1717 standard protocol and the strong performance across all 12 remaining factors. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion across all three independent modeling groups. Model risk level 3 with medium decision consequence and medium model influence yields a medium required credibility level, which is met by the overall evidence body.",
